articles.title: TCS' $2 billion agreement with Transamerica ends earlier than planned - CNBCTV18
articles.description: Both Transamerica and TCS have cited the current macro environment and respective business priorities behind the mutual termination of the deal. TCS had worked on this deal over a period of five-and-a-half years.
